com.skratchdot.riff.wav
Interface ChunkFormat

All Superinterfaces:
Chunk
All Known Implementing Classes:
ChunkFormatImpl
public interface ChunkFormat
extends Chunk

A representation of the model object 'Chunk Format'.

The following features are supported:

  • Compression Code
  • Compression Code Value
  • Number Of Channels
  • Sample Rate
  • Average Bytes Per Second
  • Block Align
  • Significant Bits Per Sample
  • Number Of Extra Format Bytes
  • Extra Format Bytes

See Also:
WavPackage.getChunkFormat()
